===荷爾蒙===
關於荷爾蒙對性傾向的影響，科學家多是針對出生前荷爾蒙研究。不少科學家相信出生前荷爾蒙是關鍵性的因素。

科學家之所以針對研究出生前荷爾蒙，是基於幾個線索：

# 從[[動物實驗|動物實驗]]上得知，實驗鼠的出生前荷爾蒙濃度會影響其性傾向。<ref>{{Cite journal|author= Kerchner M, Ward IL |title= SDN-MPOA volume in male rats is decreased by prenatal stress, but is not related to ejaculatory behavior |journal= Brain Res |volume= 581  |pages=  244-251  |year=1992 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|author= Meek LR, Schulz-Wilson KM, Keith CA |title= Effects of prenatal stress on sexual partner preference in mice |journal= Physiol Behav |volume= 89 |pages= 133-138 |year=1992 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|author= Anderson DK, Rhess RW, Fleming DE   |title= Effects of prenatal stress on differentiation    |journal=Brain Res |volume= 332 |pages= 113-118 |year=1985 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|author= Ward IL  |title=Prenatal stress feminizes and demasculinizes the behavior of males |journal=Science | volume=175 |pages= 82-84 |year=1972  }}</ref>
# 患有先天性腎上腺增生症（ CAH ，在胚胎發育期睪丸素過多[http://www.genes-at-taiwan.com.tw/genehelp/database/case/record_39.htm] {{Wayback|url=http://www.genes-at-taiwan.com.tw/genehelp/database/case/record_39.htm |date=20170505211745 }}）的女性，跟她們一些沒有患此症的女性親戚比較，前者同性戀的比率較一般女性高。<ref>{{Cite journal|author= Meyer-Bahlburg HF, Dolezal C, Baker SW, New MI|title= Sexual orientation in women with classical or non-classical congenital adrenal hyperplasis as a function of degree of prenatal androgen excess |url= https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-sexual-behavior_2008-02_37_1/page/85|journal=Arch Sex Behav |volume= 37 |pages= 85-99 |year= 2008 }}</ref>
# 研究顯示一些非性別典型的特質（包括喜好的遊戲、攻擊性、食指無名指長比、腦內SDN-POA的大小）會受到出生前荷爾蒙濃度影響。有些科學家猜想，性傾向和這些性質就好像「一個套裝」般加諸人身上。由此推論，這個「套裝」是會受到出生前荷爾蒙的濃度影響其「內涵」的。

